      "seed": 2142706093,
      "version": 674,
      "versionNonce": 1374371245,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769843237325,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. According to the process steps of the \n   task, plan and execute 2 to 3 steps each \n   time to enhance stability.\n2. E.g. If a landing situation occurs, only one \n    step needs to be planned: wait for human \n    intervention.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. According to the process steps of the \n   task, plan and execute 2 to 3 steps each \n   time to enhance stability.\n2. E.g. If a landing situation occurs, only one \n    step needs to be planned: wait for human \n    intervention.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
